    <item>
      <title>Northvolt 9.02 亿欧元的德国电池厂援助获得欧盟批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/northvolt-s-902-million-german-aid-for-battery-plant-gets-eu-ok</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典电动汽车电池开发商 Northvolt AB 获得欧盟批准，根据欧盟宽松的国家援助规则，提供近 10 亿欧元的补贴在德国建厂，该规则的部分目的是阻止美国以巨额补贴吸引欧洲公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/northvolt-s-902-million-german-aid-for-battery-plant-gets-eu-ok</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 10:48:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bet365 Boss Coates 尽管亏损但仍加薪至约 2.21 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/bet365-boss-coates-gets-pay-raise-to-280-million-despite-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Bet365 Group Ltd 创始人兼联合首席执行官丹尼斯·科茨 (Denise Coates) 在上一财年的薪水为 2.207 亿英镑（2.8 亿美元），比上一财年增长 3.4%，尽管公司陷入亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/bet365-boss-coates-gets-pay-raise-to-280-million-despite-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 10:30:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃隆·马斯克的吸毒行为是特斯拉董事会最新的头疼问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/elon-musk-drug-use-puts-tesla-board-directors-in-familiar-position</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）吸毒的报道让特斯拉公司董事会成员面临着一个熟悉的困境：必须决定如何应对首席执行官让董事和股东面临巨大的财务和法律风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/elon-musk-drug-use-puts-tesla-board-directors-in-familiar-position</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 10:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
